---
title: Rich Chicken, Bacon & Pesto Orecchiette with Green Beans & Baby Leaves
description: Orecchiette, the ‘little ears’ of pasta, are perfectly shaped to scoop up sauces and capture flavour. That’s why they’re a perfect match for this creamy pesto number, with crispy bacon, chicken and tender green beans tossed through.
